  <description><![CDATA[<p>This superior hotel has been fully renovated with modern interiors and a host of facilities for guests to enjoy. In a central location in the heart of Cortina, 6 minutes’ walk to the Faloria lift with the Ski bus stop right outside. The historic Grand Hotel Savoia welcomes guests with its first class service and fine cuisine. Facilities include bar, lounge, restaurant, lift, indoor pool, whirlpool, sauna, steam room, gym and Wi-Fi (free). Beauty treatments and massages available (pay locally).</p>]]></description>
